<h3>Building the Source</h3>
<blockquote>
To compile on linux get the source, untar it and:
<tt>
<br>./autogen.sh<br>
./configure<br>
make<br>
</tt>
<p>

You can also cross-compile to windows by:
<tt>
<br>./autogen.sh<br>
./cross-configure<br>
./cross-make<br>
</tt>
For more info on cross-compilation, look <a href="http://www.mingw.org/mingwfaq.shtml#faq-cross">here</a>.
</blockquote>
