<h3>Running Abe!!</h3>
<blockquote>
You can run it by typing <tt>./abe</tt> or <tt>abe.exe</tt> on Windows.<br>
To run in windowed mode, do: <tt>./abe --window</tt>
<tt>./abe -?</tt> will give you the less often used features.<br>
</blockquote>
